The paper proposes a new approach for designing program comprehension tools that is independent of any specific IDE, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) category. The approach involves writing annotations or special comments directly into source files, which is related to programming languages (cs.PL) and cybernetics (cs.CY). The paper also briefly evaluates the approach, which could fall under machine learning (cs.LG) or human-computer interaction (cs.HC) categories.
